法規內容.條文內容:
(1) For vessels that catch fishes, the reporting of fishing operations as referred to in Article 2 shall include the following items, and the reporting format is as shown in Appendix 1: Fishing period;
(2) Fishery type;
(3) Target species;
(4) Catch amount;
(5) Time for the sale of catch, sale amount, and buying countries;
(6) Information on the employment of nationals of the Republic of China onboard.
For carrier vessels that transport catches or fisheries products, the reporting of fishing operations as referred to in Article 2 shall include the following items, and the reporting format is as shown in Appendix 2:
(1) Transshipment period;
(2) The name and nationality of any fishing vessel wherefrom catches were transshipped;
(3) Maine species transshipped;
(4) Amount of catches or fisheries products transshipped;
(5) Information on the employment of nationals of the Republic of China onboard.
